{"tid":40400,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【三點九沈大師】大師：趁彈高位先走貨","createTime":"2016-12-15T07:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T20:19:20.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"255bfffea225e87fcc6bc8c0c7e9d338ba1325e6","tid":40400,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"【三點九沈大師】大師：趁彈高位先走貨<br />\n2016-12-15 15:31:54<br />\n<br />\n【三點九沈大師】大師：趁彈高位先走貨<br />\n<br />\n又到《三點九沈大師》時間，琴日諗住博反彈，點知今日開低啦，隊穿埋22200，到依啲位呢，我諗唔好輕舉莽動住啦，當然如果係衍生工具嘅，有啲就到期嘅，止蝕咗都冇辦法，或者如果未止蝕我就寧願等多個位，就係21957，上次特朗著當選時低位，我估計依啲位都會彈咖啦。<br />\n<br />\n寧願睇下今晚外圍，特別係美股，因為好多時美股議息後行完第二日就返轉頭，如果美股今晚可以彈一彈或者聽日埋年結或期結嘅時間可以頂高嘅話，我諗依兩日趁彈高位先走貨啦，依啲位等睇聽日有冇彈嘅力先決定喇。"},{"pid":"9456eca4cb3c07da48b991b10ed3701fe1d5f3dd","tid":40400,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"21957，上次特朗著當選時低位，我估計依啲位都會彈咖啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大師咁肯定。仆街。串撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7668385df43c06644f1259b5be8c4438d5f941","tid":40400,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"死啦，仲要跌多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cea47b27af278b7c3f70a23ad95ed57da5c760e","tid":40400,"uid":39133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"屌你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632d980f7f8d5ff239a5e4f196b16ba1300e5bba","tid":40400,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"大師點解要咁樣對我地呢d 師兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb661a3666c3e2573ee9cffe07ab2146b8f77d4","tid":40400,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ALL IN！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6ac2d682426718d1e91d720